{"tid":374052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Excel] Excel 高手請入","createTime":"2017-08-25T12:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T14:14:55.000Z","uid":102164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65c831c33b26d9002c6e1c137893e40ca718d871","tid":374052,"uid":102164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"小弟最近學左整VBA 類似做左D 自動pivot table 然後自動出pivot chart既button<br />\n但係問題黎啦 想問點樣pivot table 淨係show top 5 而唔影響個grand total 既數??<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\na 12<br />\nb 13<br />\nc 30 <br />\nd 45 <br />\ne 37<br />\nf  13<br />\n<br />\ngrand total 係150 但係如果落左value filter show top 5 grand total就會變左137<br />\n但係我純粹想show top5 唔想個grand total 變左個數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad738f3de7e422ed795c0f272213bc4558dfc298","tid":374052,"uid":102164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c9a1e770cb1008ee58b03256769dde81a6c40d","tid":374052,"uid":21548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2f7a5e1e9ecea4f85a325eba1d8382379d41aa76","tid":374052,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"唔好用pivot table lor"},{"pid":"1401ad08ba00e0fa0934e0da126f0c24373ef1a2","tid":374052,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"code係點"},{"pid":"d26d888a7629ed6d22b9183874f0ddd1ed582def","tid":374052,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"Hide咗佢得唔得？"},{"pid":"ca4aaa18cc174c2cf3b96a63c453c6905e7fee19","tid":374052,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"sum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001ca440044a012aae0b657484a362d84e20472d","tid":374052,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:48:11.000Z","msg":"簡單啲將total個 formula改做=sum(A2:F2)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時用vba反而仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d638f5a2f1fe158495001eda7905faef53538982","tid":374052,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"自動gen pivot table 即係所有數字都係for loop計出嚟？<br />\n係嘅話咪sort 咗佢 之後出頭5個 再出total<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又無code 又無data 都唔知你想點"},{"pid":"22486201b15206b6e4b2dd64578bafbdc0c73acf","tid":374052,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自動gen pivot table 即係所有數字都係for loop計出嚟？<br />\n係嘅話咪sort 咗佢 之後出頭5個 再出total<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又無code 又無data 都唔知你想點</blockquote><br />\n一係你loop 個pivot table <br />\n抽晒你要嘅data 再成個overwrite 咗佢"},{"pid":"a416e5281aad4f280e99a10b2012c0e01b841909","tid":374052,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自動gen pivot table 即係所有數字都係for loop計出嚟？<br />\n係嘅話咪sort 咗佢 之後出頭5個 再出total<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又無code 又無data 都唔知你想點</blockquote><br />\n一係你loop 個pivot table <br />\n抽晒你要嘅data 再成個overwrite 咗佢</blockquote><br />\nsort完用offset(-1,0) hide哂第五行到尾二個行其實都得"},{"pid":"9ccfcfd36f38fd8be642a612c8c656645499b0be","tid":374052,"uid":102164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自動gen pivot table 即係所有數字都係for loop計出嚟？<br />\n係嘅話咪sort 咗佢 之後出頭5個 再出total<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又無code 又無data 都唔知你想點</blockquote><br />\n一係你loop 個pivot table <br />\n抽晒你要嘅data 再成個overwrite 咗佢</blockquote><br />\nsor bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我段code 係大約做人手insert pivot table果個動作咁用 段code 用PivotFields 去做野 但value filter 開左top5 佢個total真係變左top5既sum 而唔係data range 既數"},{"pid":"2ed111c688fa26f867dc4e0dd524f8e7c5483be0","tid":374052,"uid":102164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T04:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自動gen pivot table 即係所有數字都係for loop計出嚟？<br />\n係嘅話咪sort 咗佢 之後出頭5個 再出total<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外又無code 又無data 都唔知你想點</blockquote><br />\n一係你loop 個pivot table <br />\n抽晒你要嘅data 再成個overwrite 咗佢</blockquote><br />\nsort完用offset(-1,0) hide哂第五行到尾二個行其實都得</blockquote><br />\n有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打提議"},{"pid":"08e3c2dc1c1fa42638584bafc605dab600782c65","tid":374052,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"用excel啲functions/vba會用到發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日唔明點解佢唔work"},{"pid":"58ab799071baf37600ef1a165d75a7fdaaea3945","tid":374052,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用excel啲functions/vba會用到發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日唔明點解佢唔work</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n佢d error return又on99"}]}